description: After sleeping rough for a week many migrants want to leave Lesbos, not stay in a new camp.
title: Lesbos: Greek police move migrants to new camp after Moria fire
title_page: Lesbos: Greek police move migrants to new camp after Moria fire - BBC News
maintext: Earlier, Germany also said it would take in up to 150 unaccompanied minors. Greece flew 400 children to the mainland last week, and EU countries have agreed to receive them, though the details are not yet clear.
